<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthy Lifestyle Tips</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/lifestyle.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="maincontainer">
        {{>navbar}}
        <header>
            <h1><span id="element"></span></h1>
        </header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Stay Hydrated</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Drink plenty of water throughout the day to stay properly hydrated.</li>
                    <li>Limit sugary drinks and excessive caffeine.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Eat a Balanced Diet</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Eat a variety of nutrient-rich foods, including fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins,
                        and
                        healthy fats.</li>
                    <li>Limit processed foods, sugary snacks, and high-calorie, low-nutrient items.
                        Practice portion control to avoid overeating</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Regular Physical Activity</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Aim for at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity or 75 minutes of
                        vigorous-intensity activity per week.</li>
                    <li>Include strength training exercises to build and maintain muscle mass.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Adequate Sleep</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Prioritize getting 7-9 hours of quality sleep each night.</li>
                    <li>Create a calming bedtime routine and maintain a consistent sleep schedule.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Stress Management</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Practice stress-reduction techniques such as deep breathing, meditation, yoga, or mindfulness.
                    </li>
                    <li>Engage in activities you enjoy to unwind and relax.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Social Connections</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cultivate strong relationships with friends, family, and a supportive social network.</li>
                    <li>Spend quality time with loved ones and engage in social activities.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Mindful Eating</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Eat slowly, paying attention to your body's hunger and fullness cues.</li>
                    <li>Avoid distractions like screens while eating to fully savor your meals.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Stay Hydrated</h2>
                <p>Drink plenty of water throughout the day to keep your body hydrated and support overall health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Limit Screen Time</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Set boundaries for screen time, especially before bedtime.</li>
                    <li>Balance screen activities with physical activities and face-to-face interactions.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Regular Health Check-ups</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Schedule routine medical check-ups to monitor your health and catch potential issues early.</li>
                    <li>Follow your doctor's recommendations for screenings and vaccinations.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Limit Alcohol and Tobacco</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>If you drink alcohol, do so in moderation. Avoid excessive drinking.</li>
                    <li>Avoid tobacco products altogether. If you smoke, seek help to quit.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Practice Gratitude</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cultivate a positive outlook by acknowledging and appreciating the good things in your life.
                    </li>
                    <li>Keep a gratitude journal to record moments of thankfulness.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Hobbies and Recreation</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Engage in hobbies and activities that bring you joy and fulfillment.</li>
                    <li>Allocate time for leisure and creative pursuits.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Hygiene and Self-Care</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Maintain good personal hygiene habits, including regular bathing and dental care.</li>
                    <li>Prioritize self-care activities that make you feel rejuvenated.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Environmental Wellness</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create a clean, organized, and comfortable living environment that promotes well-being.</li>
                    <li>Incorporate elements of nature, such as houseplants, to improve indoor air quality.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2>Practice Safe Habits</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Wear seat belts while driving and use protective gear during physical activities.</li>
                    <li>Take precautions to prevent accidents and injuries.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more tips as needed -->
        </div>
        {{footer}}
    </div>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/typed.js@2.0.16/dist/typed.umd.js"></script>
    <script>
        var typed = new Typed('#element', {
            strings: ['Healthy Lifestyle Tips'],
            typeSpeed: 50,
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>